  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "TECHNICIAN",
  "description": "<h3><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></h3><p>The incumbent is responsible for carrying out the assigned tasks in laboratory to support the achievement of the sales targets. In addition, the incumbent is to ensure the testing meets the ISO/IEC 17025 requirement and tests according to relevant standard and specification to fulfil the client/customer requirements.</p><p><u><strong>Samples/Works Preparation</strong></u></p><p>• Receive samples from clients and check against the request form:</p><p>- Quantity,</p><p>- Test standards,</p><p>- Contact person,</p><p>- Bill party & company details</p><p>- Check the request form details is complete</p><p>-Acknowledgment receipt to client</p><p>• Store the samples at receiving area for testing:</p><p>- Check and ensure that samples are correctly labelled as per request form</p><p>- Check and ensure environmental conditions are as per test standard where required</p><p>• Prepare the samples for testing according to the test standards:</p><p>- Carry out safety checks and risk assessment</p><p>- Sample shape and size</p><p>-\nConditioning of samples where required</p><p>- Perform pre-testing procedures where required</p><p>- Prepare datasheet</p><p><u><strong>Samples Testing & Reports</strong></u></p><p>• Setup of appropriate testing equipment and environment</p><p>• Conduct the test according to test standards and or SOP</p><p>• Observe and record the test results, and take actions where needed:</p><p>- Complete the datasheet</p><p>- Pass samples are dispose or return to client</p><p>- Fail samples be kept according to test standards and or SOP</p><p>- Re-test where required</p><p>• Prepare official test report for checking and endorsement</p><p><u><strong>Equipment and Work Area Maintenance</strong></u></p><p>• Maintain the test equipment according to schedules:</p><p>- Cleaning, greasing and oiling of equipment</p><p>- Replacement of consumables</p><p>- Repair where required and inform superior</p><p>- Monitor equipment calibration schedules</p><p><u><strong>Reporting</strong></u></p><p>• Increase the commitments on doing the report and submit it to ERS system</p><p>Client Dealing</p><p>• Deal with client for the sample receiving and witness tests</p>",
